{"tid":2231844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為佳仔平反","createTime":"2020-10-06T03:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T08:29:39.000Z","uid":29969,"like":10,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dea98f7aed637fd0e8325643848fd246fd92418b","tid":2231844,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:21:18.000Z","msg":"平你老味反死殺人犯<br />\n啲連登仔講到條女派帽<br />\n十惡不赦死有餘辜咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁係咪全世界派帽既就殺得<br />\n咁男人出軌又點計<br />\n<br />\n出面有啲連登仔又拉埋左膠女權撚黎講<br />\n你價值觀咁岩 唔岩聽殺哂啲人都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果陳同佳有上連登<br />\n見到有人幫佢講好說話實笑出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後想講陳同佳屌你老母殺人犯<br />\n搞咁多野出黎真係死10次都唔夠"},{"pid":"4d16539eef70b1b094a97935e9fe16b53d465f57","tid":2231844,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:26:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcaa452b874925e4001be6d5cc11c24afa06557e","tid":2231844,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dbf5ce8ba3afdc3d76e23564eb447fa68918b29","tid":2231844,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"1. 佢殺條女 道德上一定錯<br />\n2. 無打算幫佢平反<br />\n3. 中共搵藉口推 唔係陳同佳 都會有第二個「導火線」"},{"pid":"c27f1f6e21faae430710dff9208fb5e0a91c7000","tid":2231844,"uid":29969,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dbf5ce8ba3afdc3d76e23564eb447fa68918b29","tid":2231844,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:30:46.000Z","msg":"1. 佢殺條女 道德上一定錯<br />\n2. 無打算幫佢平反<br />\n3. 中共搵藉口推 唔係陳同佳 都會有第二個「導火線」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfngfsN